\"to\": 687}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in the coastal city of Durban, the 32-year-old is one of seven African break dancers - known as B-girls and B-boys -- vying to make it to Paris.\", \"from\": 744, \"to\": 893, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 772, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 8.487913837509593e-13, \"text\": \"Durban\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Durban\"}, {\"begin\": 887, \"end\": 892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.6598689716758174e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the coastal city\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 768}, {\"ngram\": \"seven African break dancers\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 833}, {\"ngram\": \"B-girls\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 852}, {\"ngram\": \"B\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 858}, {\"ngram\": \"-boys\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Along with a fellow South African B-girl, she is hoping to catch a break in upcoming qualifiers in Shanghai and Budapest.\", \"from\": 895, \"to\": 1016, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 994, \"end\": 1002, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"score\": 0.9999999987726369, \"rank\": 1.0789526964784319e-09, \"text\": \"Shanghai\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shanghai\"}, {\"begin\": 1007, \"end\": 1015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999999831093193, \"rank\": 1.6885116829493167e-08, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fellow South African B-girl\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 960, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"upcoming qualifiers\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paul said she got into breakdancing almost by chance, having previously practised gymnastics, kickboxing, Muay Thai and other sports.\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1124, \"end\": 1133, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\", \"score\": 0.7547153317019676, \"rank\": 0.32500289578732017, \"text\": \"Muay Thai\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kickboxing\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paul\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1022}, {\"ngram\": \"chance\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1070}, {\"ngram\": \"gymnastics\", \"from\": 1100, \"to\": 1110}, {\"ngram\": \"kickboxing\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1150}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After moving to Johannesburg dreaming of a professional dancing career, she started working as a choreographer as well as backup dancer, DJ and media entrepreneur.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a professional dancing career\", \"from\": 1194, \"to\": 1223}, {\"ngram\": \"a choreographer\", \"from\": 1248, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"backup dancer\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"DJ\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"media entrepreneur\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decades-old street dance style always appealed to her but she practised mostly as a hobby, \\\"doing nonsense until it formed into something\\\" thinking nothing much would come out of it.\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decades-old street dance style\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"a hobby\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1411}, {\"ngram\": \"nonsense\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1428}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1459}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was nowhere for me to take it - no platforms existed,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no platforms\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1557}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then in 2020, the coronavirus pandemic hit with its lockdowns, giving Paul ample time to dedicate to her passion.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the coronavirus\", \"from\": 1593, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"pandemic\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"its lockdowns\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1640}, {\"ngram\": \"Paul\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"ample time\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1664}, {\"ngram\": \"her passion\", \"from\": 1680, \"to\": 1691}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was God's way of saying: \\\"Let us get you back to the thing we want you to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1694, \"to\": 1785, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"God's way\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1710}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1727, \"to\": 1729}, {\"ngram\": \"the thing\", \"from\": 1746, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I'd like to have been, you know, six years younger, but I will take what I can get.\\\"\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1872, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'Explosive, powerful lady'She developed a unique style, which she describes as a mixture of her self-starter \\\"roughness\\\", \\\"education\\\" and \\\"South African flavour\\\".\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"powerful lady'She\", \"from\": 1886, \"to\": 1903}, {\"ngram\": \"a unique style\", \"from\": 1914, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"a mixture\", \"from\": 1953, \"to\": 1962}, {\"ngram\": \"her self-starter \\\"roughness\", \"from\": 1966, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"education\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"South African flavour\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2034}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her trainer, Jaco Claasen, described her during a session as an \\\"explosive\\\" and \\\"powerful lady\\\" who literally throws herself into her moves.\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her trainer\", \"from\": 2038, \"to\": 2049}, {\"ngram\": \"Jaco Claasen\", \"from\": 2051, \"to\": 2063}, {\"ngram\": \"a session\", \"from\": 2086, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"powerful lady\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2132}, {\"ngram\": \"her moves\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2177}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In preparation for the Olympics, he said much of the work will go to fine-tuning her stability and muscle connection to handle the force.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2194}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2199, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2237}, {\"ngram\": \"her stability\", \"from\": 2261, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"muscle connection\", \"from\": 2279, \"to\": 2296}, {\"ngram\": \"the force\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Forty other female dancers from across the world are taking part in qualifiers this month and the next.\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2422, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Forty other female dancers\", \"from\": 2319, \"to\": 2345}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2367}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2383}, {\"ngram\": \"qualifiers\", \"from\": 2387, \"to\": 2397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Only 16 will go to Paris.\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2449, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2443, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.6598689716758174e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There they will battle it out for gold through four one-on-one clashes or throwdowns, lasting up to 60 seconds.\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 2485, \"to\": 2489}, {\"ngram\": \"four one-on-one clashes\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2521}, {\"ngram\": \"throwdowns\", \"from\": 2525, \"to\": 2535}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 60 seconds\", \"from\": 2545, \"to\": 2561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A DJ will choose the beat.\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2589, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2565, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"score\": 0.9999999966198629, \"rank\": 2.598667267651329e-09, \"text\": \"DJ\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Disc_jockey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beat\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2588}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their performance will be ranked based on criterias including technique, musicality and originality.\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their performance\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2608}, {\"ngram\": \"criterias\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"technique\", \"from\": 2653, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"musicality\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2674}, {\"ngram\": \"originality\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paul said she was astounded when she learnt Paris was on the cards.\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2760, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2737, \"end\": 2742, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.6598689716758174e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Paul\", \"from\": 2693, \"to\": 2697}, {\"ngram\": \"the cards\", \"from\": 2750, \"to\": 2759}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Breaking has been added as an official Olympic sport,\\\" she recalled a friend telling her.\", \"from\": 2762, \"to\": 2852, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Breaking\", \"from\": 2763, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"an official Olympic sport\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2815}, {\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 2831, \"to\": 2839}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could not believe it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2878, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But chasing her dream has not been easy as the nascent sport is yet to attract enough big sponsorships.\", \"from\": 2880, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her dream\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2901}, {\"ngram\": \"the nascent sport\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"enough big sponsorships\", \"from\": 2959, \"to\": 2982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Nine out of 10 times, everything is coming out of my pocket,\\\" said Paul, adding she can compete in only a handful of events a year, lacking the money to travel more.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"10 times\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3018}, {\"ngram\": \"my pocket\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3045}, {\"ngram\": \"Paul\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3057}, {\"ngram\": \"only a handful\", \"from\": 3085, \"to\": 3099}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3109}, {\"ngram\": \"the money\", \"from\": 3126, \"to\": 3135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In a perfect world, I'd be a professional athlete and get paid to train, eat and sleep, unfortunately in South Africa, that's not my reality.\\\"\", \"from\": 3153, \"to\": 3296, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3259, \"end\": 3271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9998588234162706, \"rank\": 0.0001411840097221271, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a perfect world\", \"from\": 3157, \"to\": 3172}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional athlete\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3203}, {\"ngram\": \"my reality\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic visibility is hopefully going to change that, making life easier for future athletes, she said.\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3401, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic visibility\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3316}, {\"ngram\": \"life\", \"from\": 3359, \"to\": 3363}, {\"ngram\": \"future athletes\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The circuits that have been built around Olympic qualifiers are game-changing,\\\" Paul said.\", \"from\": 3403, \"to\": 3494, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The circuits\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3416}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic qualifiers\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3463}, {\"ngram\": \"Paul\", \"from\": 3484, \"to\": 3488}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have worked as hard as I can, and I am as ready as I can be.\", \"from\": 3496, \"to\": 3559, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A self-assured person is a dangerous one!\\\"\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A self-assured person\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"a dangerous one\", \"from\": 3585, \"to\": 3600}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Source:AFP \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9 2026.\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Source\", \"from\": 3604, \"to\": 3610}, {\"ngram\": \"AFP \\u00a9 RT\\u00c9\", \"from\": 3611, \"to\": 3620}]}, {\"sentence\": \"RT\\u00c9.ie is the website of Raidi\\u00f3 Teilif\\u00eds \\u00c9ireann, Ireland's National Public Service Media.\",